      Extended typical nonlinear oscillator equation form:

        y = a0 * x0                      # linear restoring force ~ position
          + a1 * x1                      # linear damping ~ velocity
          + a2 * (x0 ** 3)               # cubic stiffness nonlinearity (Duffing)
          + a3 * (x1 ** 3)               # cubic nonlinear damping
